properties.City:
On our first experience at Bilkent Labs, we're cheerful, hope this continuos likewise. This was the caption
                of my instagram post in the Bilkent Labs using an oscillisocope for the first time. Though there has been sleeples 
                nights in those labs throughout four years of my Bachelors degree, the feeling when I received my Bachelor of Science
                degree is unspeakble after four years of hustling. I was the type of person who had to go home after a nighout because
                I had to study... Having graduated with an honors degree, I can safely say that I'd do all over again the same way!
